reviews.review_text:
- Another slightly harsh, relatively OK recording, but the best available: have fun with the EQ. 

Jerry's guitar is horribly out of tune in Row Jimmy. What a crime! Talk about hemispheres out of phase! 

Yeah, in all, hard to hold on through the sound. Maybe the venue was having troubles too, although I think the Frost has a good reputation...?
